      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a meticulously maintained E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power plant delivers 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline, channeled through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping characteristics. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the mechanical integrity of the independent throttle body assembly. The exterior retains its factory luster with minor patina consistent with spirited enthusiast use. Riding on staggered 19-inch Style 220M forged wheels, this M3 offers an unfiltered longitudinal and lateral driving experience. A prime example of BMW M\u2019s high-revving atmospheric era, ready for the B-roads.",
