      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained sedan that perfectly balances refined luxury with everyday dependability. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy luster, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a few faint surface marks consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather seats remain supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, while all wood-trim accents remain crack-free. Every onboard system, including the intuitive navigation and the premium surround-sound audio, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule\u2014a full portfolio of maintenance records is included. With a set of high-tread tires and recently serviced brakes, this car offers a confident, turn-key driving experience for a discerning buyer who values mechanical integrity and documented care.",
